Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.streams.interfaces

Interface JsonSaxDeserializer<T>

Type Parameters:
T - class instance to manipulate with the interface
All Superinterfaces:
JsonSaxHandler
public interface JsonSaxDeserializer<T>
extends JsonSaxHandler

This interface extends JsonSaxHandler interface to support automatic deserialization from JSON to Java classes.

Since:
0.0.1
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
JsonSaxParser, RFC 7159

  • Method Details

    • use

      void use​(T instance)

      Use the given instance of the class to fill deserialized data to.

      Parameters:
      instance - instance to fill data from the JSON. Call with the null parameter guarantees, that the new class instance will be created instead of filling existent class instance

    • getInstance

      T getInstance()

      Get class instance with the deserialized data. It can be new instance on the same first parsing or calling use(Object) with the null parameter, or class instance returned on previous parsing, or class instance explicitly passed by calling use(Object).

      Returns:
      instance deserialized
